The paper is about the design of cryptographic algorithms, specifically the design of Substitution Boxes (S-boxes). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves analysis of fitness landscapes, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity). Additionally, the use of heuristics in designing S-boxes could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
